According to the screen image, the icon of Firefox browser is located in the center of the desktop. To open the Firefox browser by double clicking, we need to move the mouse over the icon, and then double click.
The following are the corresponding JSON format actions:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "double_click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 534, "height": 360}}
]
```
